## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available online resources, which may not cover all aspects of the topic comprehensively. The influence of society on behavior is a complex and multifaceted subject that can vary significantly across different cultures and social contexts. Additionally, the sources used may reflect certain biases or limitations inherent in their perspectives. Further research, including empirical studies and cross-cultural analyses, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic.